item.title: 100 Compile Errors
item.dc:creator: @TeleNubby TeleNubby
item.description:
@TeleNubby wrote:

You missed a bracket somewhere.

That’s all that we can help with, since it’s limited to 100 errors. Make backups next time. You can also try something that checks brackets and tells if you are missing one. Maybe something like TextPad, I’m not sure. But in a situation like yours, you cant find the spot you missed the bracket just by looking at the error log.
